metadata.name: The Cherry Fox
metadata.description:
“The Cherry Fox” 2020  
 Improvise freestyle drawing with colored pencils, and ink on paper,  26 × 37 cm

ButterRabbitz is a Thai woman street artist that is obsessed with colored pencil painting techniques. Because this approach demands great talent and a lot of time, finding somebody with the same experience is difficult. However, it contrasts with the character of street artists, who frequently use spraying techniques or paint quickly within a time limit. This young artist frequently has creative techniques that surprise art lovers, and she has many fans who follow her work continuously.
